ReadESM changelog
2018.1
* Update manufacturers
* Update Spain Region Codes: add support for Ceuta and Melilla
* Update nation codes: add support for Tajikistan
* Add support for ISO/IEC 8859-7 "Latin/Greek" encoded fields
* Fix bug #4 "Problem showing Help page on readesm-2011.12pre1"
* Fix bugs #6 and #8: BCDs are parsed as big endian integers
* Fix bug #7 "CardDriverActivity::readCyclicData() algorithm loses data"
* Fix bug #9 "Premature end of document"
* Fix bug: Uninitialized read in HtmlReporter
* Fix bug: Manufacturer specific types in EventFaultRecordPurpose not recognized
* Fix bug: following anchor links in a report in ReadESM leads to errors or blank pages
* Fix minor memory leaks
* Migrate from Qt4 to Qt5
* Migrate from QWebKit to QWebEngine
* More documentation
* Lots of minor optimizations, spelling fixes, HTML fixes, link fixes, code hardening and cleanups
* Translation updates
* Stricter adherence to standards and conventions
* Drop compatibility with Netscape Navigator 4

2011-11
+ optical fixes

2011-10
+ Lots of internal changes
+ Monthly Timesheets
+ More Accurate visualization of Driver activities, added "unknown" state
+ Show textual representation of activities on demand
+ Should read more files without crashing
+ Hungarian translation, thanks to Mikulás Róbert
0 Read and show all data, this of course makes it a bit harder to read
0 Use lists instead of tables in html output
- No more plaintext output
- No more classic html output, so generated files cannot be read in old versions of IE
- Content section at start of generated html has less links


2011-04(preliminary, svn)
* Spanish translation, thanks to Jose Huguet
* decode extended serial number
* decode vehicle registration numbers correctly, italian numbers no longer 
  cause invalid files 
* Crashes no longer if the last block on a tachograph card file has no signature
* fixed vanishing first character of some strings (vehicle number etc.)
* axis labels for svg graphs
* produced xhtml files have cleaner whitespace and smaller size
* created icon
* Linux: register mimetype, create menu entry, associate files

2011-03a
* more german translation (more or less complete)
* fixed a bug where readesm reserved one gigabyte of memory to read a file

2011-03
* fixed more bugs resulting from the QT transition

2011-03pre1
* Transition to the QT framework
* Transition to cmake
* New graphical user interface

0.3.2
* more bug fixes

0.3.1
* fixed bug with readesm-wrap-kde using the wrong prefix

0.3.0
* Transition to sourceforge

no changelog available for older releases
